    "title": "标签管理",
    "author": "hua",
    "updateDate": 1490155632351,
    "content": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"></span></p><hr/><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://ueditor.baidu.com/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" alt=\"*\"/>标签分客户、工单、会话、客服技能四种，管理员可以在后台新建标签，客服也可以自己在相应页面添加标签，管理员可以随时维护标签库，进行统一管理。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">    <img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-4-4-1.png\"><br/></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">    添加标签</h2><hr/><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">管理员微上客，进入设置后台---标签管理，点击（+）添加标签，标签可添加多级标签</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">提供标签重新编辑，及删除标签</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-4-4-2.png\"></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">会话标签：每个条会话都可以贴标签，鼠标移动到会话，</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">会出现⋯点击添加标签即可</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">工单标签：创建工单时，直接在工单名称旁+添加标签</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">客户标签：不论什么渠道来的客户，在上方客户基本信息处可</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">给该客户添加标签</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">客服技能标签：添加客服技能标签后，客户发送的消息会先检索匹配客服技能标签，优先将会话发送给对应客服</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>"
}